Gerald G. Ermentrout



Mr. Gerald G. Ermentrout is on the Board of Directors at KMG Chemicals, Inc. Mr. Ermentrout was previously employed as Independent Non-Executive Director by AZ Electronic Materials SA and VP & General Manager-Electronic Chemicals Division by Air Products & Chemicals, Inc. He also served on the board at AZ Electronic Materials USA Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from United States Naval Academy and an MBA from Lehigh University.



