Gerald G. Ermentrout  Lead Director , KMG Chemicals, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships69$135,451
Background

		Mr. Gerald G. Ermentrout, also known as Gerry, served as Vice President and General Manager of Electronic Division Air Products & Chemicals, Inc. from 1996 to 2007. Mr. Ermentrout has over 30 years of experience in industrial gases and electronic chemicals. During his tenure at Air Products, he also held positions where he managed oxygen, nitrogen and hydrogen plants and pipeline systems, as well as managed major acquisitions and divestitures. Mr. Ermentrout joined Air ... Products and Chemicals, Inc. in 1975 and held various positions until his retirement in early 2007. He managed Air Products' global materials and equipment business serving the semiconductor and flat panel display industries, with responsibility for sales, marketing and operations. He has many years of experience of the global electronic chemicals industry having held both executive and non-executive director positions in US based international businesses. He serves as a Lead Director of KMG Chemicals Inc., and has been its Director since May 28, 2008. He has been an Independent Non-Executive Director at AZ Electronic Materials S.A. since October 28, 2010. Mr. Ermentrout received a Bachelor of Science in Engineering from the US Naval Academy and a Masters of Business Administration from Lehigh University.Read Full Background




